recital.p:
Following an application from H.J. Heinz Supply Chain Europe B.V., submitted pursuant to Article 14(1)(b) of Regulation (EC) No 1924/2006, the Authority was required to deliver an opinion on a health claim related to 'Nutrimune®' and immune defence against pathogens in the gastrointestinal tract and upper respiratory tract (Question No EFSA-Q-2016-00008


                        EFSA Journal 2017;15(1):4679.
                  ). The claim proposed by the applicant was worded as follows: '"Nutrimune®" supports the immune defence in the gastrointestinal and upper respiratory tract of young children'.
